(49, 49, 27446, '[#27446] Fix: can not dump multiple objects contained in the session', 'When the session contains multiple objects, only the first object can be "unfolded" while the other(s) are displayed but can not be "opened" caused by a wrong id.\r<br>\r<br>**Test:**\r<br>\r<br>```php\r<br><?php\r<br>$foo = new stdClass;\r<br>$foo->bar = ''baz'';\r<br>$_SESSION[''foo''] = $foo;\r<br>```\r<br>\r<br>joomlacode.org tracker: [#27446](http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&tracker_item_id=27446)\r<br>', 3, 0, 10, '2011-12-20 22:56:59', '2012-06-25 14:14:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/49.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
