(126, 126, NULL, 'Installation issue if session.save_handler is set to "sqlite"', 'Cannot install Joomla 2.51 if session.save_handler is set to sqlite and session.save_path is session.sdb. It seens Joomla do not recognize this option for sessions correctly:\r<br>\r<br>Failed to write session data (files). Please verify that the current setting of session.save_path is correct (C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Zend\\ZendServer\\tmp\\session.sdb)\r<br>...\r<br>open(C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Zend\\ZendServer\\tmp\\session.sdb\\sess_m8rsoc9q6ap2nsh9jkelrfdqb3, O_RDWR) fa\r<br>...\r<br>\r<br>So far i had no issues with this PHP Settings.\r<br>\r<br>I have now set both to standard values with ini_set (files,tmp path), now everything works fine. ', 3, 0, 1, '2012-02-11 01:44:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
