(166, 166, NULL, 'PostgreSQL driver for Joomla! CMS. [v2] - [DEPRECATED]', 'This driver implements inherited function from JDatabase class and add some other useful function to be able to use Joomla! on PostgreSQL database.\r<br>There is also a class that inherits from JDatabaseQuery to be able to create query object using PostgreSQL dialect.\r<br>Also added change item class for Postgresql under CMS libraries folder.\r<br>This pull include codes from platform 12.1 for JDatabaseQuery::charLength to address CMS'' CASE WHEN\r<br>queries that has to be compared with 0 .\r<br>\r<br>JDatabasePostgresql::getQuery has an optional second parameter to retrieve JDatabasePostgresqlQuery object, used inside JDatabasePostgresql::insertid call .\r<br>\r<br>PostgreSQL''s added functions:\r<br>- getRandom, ge a random number\r<br>- getStringPositionSQL, returns string''s position inside another string\r<br>- releaseTransactionSavepoint, release given savepoint during transaction\r<br>- showTables, lists all table in database\r<br>- transactionSavepoint, to create a savepoint\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>Overridden functions:\r<br>- connected\r<br>- dropTable\r<br>- escape\r<br>- explain \r<br>- fetchArray\r<br>- fetchAssoc\r<br>- fetchObject\r<br>- freeResult\r<br>- getAffectedRows\r<br>- getAlterDbCharacterSet\r<br>- getCollation\r<br>- getCreateDbQuery\r<br>- getNumRows\r<br>- getQuery\r<br>- getTableColumns\r<br>- getTableCreate\r<br>- getTableKeys\r<br>- getTableList\r<br>- getVersion\r<br>- hasUTF\r<br>- insertid\r<br>- insertObject\r<br>- lockTable\r<br>- query\r<br>- queryBatch\r<br>- renameTable\r<br>- replacePrefix\r<br>- select\r<br>- setUTF\r<br>- test\r<br>- transactionCommit\r<br>- transactionRollback\r<br>- transactionStart\r<br>- unlockTables\r<br>- updateObject\r<br>\r<br>PostgreSQL database query added functions:\r<br>- limit, a possible replace for limit in setQuery\r<br>- offset, a possible replace for limit in setQuery\r<br>- forShare, lock table/row during SELECT\r<br>- forUpdate, lock table/row during SELECT\r<br>- noWait, no wait a locked table\r<br>- returning, an INSERT INTO optional clause to returns last insert id', 3, 0, 1, '2012-03-25 17:50:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/166.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
