(228, 228, NULL, 'com_media: Auto-fill Image URL after upload', 'com_media is great, but uploading several images and having to find each one in the imagelist is a pain. This pull request addresses that issue by auto-filling the image url after successful upload via JApplication::setUserState() and JApplication::getUserState()<br><br>This solves tracker item - http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&tracker_item_id=28624', 3, 0, 1, '2012-06-06 12:29:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/228.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
