(234, 234, NULL, 'Advanced ACL for com_modules, permissions per module', 'I noticed that a lot of people that are using the Joomla ACL system are looking for permission support per module and not just for the entire com_modules component. <br><br>This patch adds advanced ACL to com_modules and allows to set permissions (delete, edit & edit.state) per module. ', 3, 0, 1, '2012-06-08 09:48:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/234.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
