(244, 244, NULL, 'FinderController duplicate lines', 'In FinderController (/components/com_finder/controller.php), the following lines appear twice:<br><br><br>		// Load plug-in language files.<br>		FinderHelperLanguage::loadPluginLanguage();<br><br>First on lines 43+44 then immediately after on lines 46+47.<br><br>Also, line 41 sets $user = JFactory::getUser(); but $user is never used in this function so the line can be removed. ', 3, 0, 1, '2012-06-18 07:29:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
