(258, 258, NULL, 'Menu Manager: Edit Menu Item - Default Page option for Default Menu Link is unlogical ', 'Situation:<br>1. Create a bunch of Menu Items<br>2. Set one of them(e.g. Home) as "Default Page"<br>3. Now open them Menu Item:Home(Menu Manager: Edit Menu Item - View)<br>4. Try to set the "Default Page" to "No"<br><br>The result:<br>Save failed with the following error: At least one menu item has to be set as Default.<br><br>Solution maybe:<br>Maybe a checkbox, remove the decission between yes or no!<br><br>Best regards', 3, 0, 1, '2012-07-01 10:13:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
