(363, 363, NULL, 'Removes <strong> from module chrome markup', '<strong> is a semantic element, not a presentational one. For stylistic purposes simply set font-weight in css instead. It''s use in this context is incorrect.<br><br>See: http://html5doctor.com/i-b-em-strong-element/ for details.<br><br>Semantically, it would be preferable to wrap the module header in a <header> element too of course.<br><br>I shall submit an additional PR with suggested improvements to the module markup. <br><br>Thanks.', 3, 0, 10, '2012-09-07 08:43:26', '2012-09-07 09:10:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/363.diff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
