(408, 408, NULL, 'com_contact single contact view for logged-in user', 'I believe that the single contact view for com_contact should also allow the display of the contact information attached to the logged in user, because the contact component is more flexible than the profile plugin.<br><br>The fix is easy:<br>* make the user field in the contact menu item optional<br>* default to the logged in user''s ID<br>* only throw error if neither of the IDs is defined (from the request trough menu item params or from the session from the logged-in user)', 3, 0, 1, '2012-09-18 08:54:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
